i. Here are the possible outcomes in each of the two events:
       A={(BGB), (GGB), (BGG), (GGG)}
       C={(BBB), (GGG)}
 ii. The two events overlap, they have the outcome (GGG) in common.
 iii. Based on ii, the events are not disjoint since they can happen together, if the couple ends up having three girls.  
